  <sect1 id="twitux-getting-started"> 
    <title>Getting Started</title> 

    <sect2 id="twitux-start">
    <title>To Start &app;</title>
    <para>You can start <application>&app;</application> in the following ways:
    </para> 
    <variablelist>
    	<varlistentry>
    		<term><guimenu>Applications</guimenu> menu</term>
    		<listitem>
    		  <para>Choose 
    		    <menuchoice>
    		      <guisubmenu>Internet</guisubmenu>
    		      <guimenuitem>Twitux</guimenuitem>
    		    </menuchoice>.
                  </para>
    		</listitem>
    	</varlistentry>
    	<varlistentry>
    		<term>Command line</term>
    		<listitem>
    		<para>
			To start <application>&app;</application> from a command line,
			type <command>twitux</command> and then press <keycap>Return</keycap>.
		</para>
    		</listitem>
    	</varlistentry>
    </variablelist>
    </sect2>
    
    <sect2 id="twitux-start-first">
      <title>When You Start &app; the First Time</title>
      <para>
	When you start <application>&app;</application> the first time, you will be
	shown the <interface>Twitter Account</interface> dialog, so that you can set
	up your	Twitter account credentials.
      </para>
      <orderedlist>
        <listitem>
	  <itemizedlist>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>Enter your Twitter <guilabel>Username</guilabel>.</para>
	    </listitem>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>Enter your Twitter <guilabel>Password</guilabel>.</para>
	    </listitem>
	    <listitem>
	      <para>
		Select <guilabel>Show Password</guilabel> if you wish you
		to have your password visible in the
		<interface>Twitter Account</interface> dialog.
	      </para>
	    </listitem>
	  </itemizedlist>
	</listitem>
      </orderedlist>
    </sect2>	

